Home will display all character statistics
Character:
    - Level
    - Experience (progress bar and numeric display)
    - Skill points (unspent / total)
    - Strength (multiplier to weapon damage)
    - Speed (multiplier to weapon speed)
    - Endurance (multiplier to armor protection)
    - Vitality (multiplier to armor life)
    - Piety (multiplier to prayer)
    - Divinity (Loose counter of prayers - negatively affects future prayers. Loosely offset by Piety)
Character Calculated: (these values will come from allocated skill points on the skill tree)
    - Damage increase
    - Life increase
    - Protection increase
    - Speed increase
Resources:
    - Gold
Forging Materials:
    - Iron
    - Quartz
    - Rubies
    - Sapphire
    - Emeralds
    - Topaz